data.description: This New manufactured home boast it all. You instantly feel at home when you walk through the door. It is equipped with gently used stainless steel appliances. Vaulted ceilings, extra insulation, Thermal paned windows along with brow windows for that extra ray of sunshine and a large 20x12 wood deck.  A 20x28 metal 2 car garage equip with automatic garage door. Brand new water treatment system. There is an area completely fenced in the backyard with 2 gates. This property offers privacy and a serene Stillness. This property is being sold with1.14 acres.
